{ Forcing Black to either give up the protection of the d8-square or move his bishop to a worse square. }
18... Bd6 19. Be3
{ After kicking Black's bishop to a worse square, we return our own bishop to a more active place. }
19... b6 20. Rg6 Bb7
{ Black rushes to capture our trapped knight but it won't help. } 21. Nxb6 axb6
22. Rgxd6 Nxd6 23. Rxd6
{ Black has lost too many pawns to reach an endgame of opposite coloured bishops. Also, because the rooks are still present, this endgame cannot be held. }
