5... exd4 { Black can try opening the center. } 6. Nxd4 Nc5
{ This is too early. } 7. g5 { Black's position will collapse soon. } 7... Nfd7
{ This makes no sense, after 6... Nc5 Blacks idea must be to capture on e4. }
8. Be3 Ne5 9. f4 { White is just gaining space and time. } 9... Bg4 10. Be2
Bxe2 11. Qxe2
{ Black still needs to retreat, while White is ready to castle long and break the center with all pieces developed and ready to attack. }
